  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_royal_college_of_general_practitioners">Royal College of General Practitioners</xref>
 is an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_royal_college_of_general_practitioners">Royal College of General Practitioners</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_royal_college_of_general_practitioners">RCGP</xref>) is the professional membership body for family doctors in the UK and abroad.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_royal_college_of_general_practitioners">Royal College of General Practitioners</xref>
 is committed to improving 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 care, clinical standards and 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_general_practitioner">GENERAL PRACTITIONER</xref>
 training.        </p>
      <p>
For further information on the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_royal_college_of_general_practitioners">Royal College of General Practitioners</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_royal_college_of_general_practitioners">Royal College of General Practitioners</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.rcgp.org.uk/about-us.aspx"
               scope="external"
               format="html">About us</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
